  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(230, 230, 230)\">The Iron Suitor</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_dance_with_dragons\" title=\"A dance with dragons\"><img alt=\"ADanceWithDragons.jpg\" src=\"/images/7/79/ADanceWithDragons.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"337\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Isle_of_Cedars\" title=\"Isle of Cedars\">Isle of Cedars</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n741 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(230, 230, 230)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_29\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 29\">The Reaver</a><br /><i>A Feast for Crows</i><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_55\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 55\">The Queensguard</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\">The Iron Suitor</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_57\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 57\">Tyrion XI</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_63\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 63\">Victarion I</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Characters_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_56&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Lukasz_Jaskolski_VictarionGreyjoyhandII.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/74/Lukasz_Jaskolski_VictarionGreyjoyhandII.png/350px-Lukasz_Jaskolski_VictarionGreyjoyhandII.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"223\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/74/Lukasz_Jaskolski_VictarionGreyjoyhandII.png/525px-Lukasz_Jaskolski_VictarionGreyjoyhandII.png 1.5x, /images/7/74/Lukasz_Jaskolski_VictarionGreyjoyhandII.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Lukasz_Jaskolski_VictarionGreyjoyhandII.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a>'s charred hand, by by Lukasz Jaskolski © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a> is anchored near the <a href=\"/index.php/Isle_of_Cedars\" title=\"Isle of Cedars\">Isle of Cedars</a>, right outside <a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a>, to find <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>. He was sent by his brother, King <a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Euron Greyjoy</a>, to command the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Fleet\" title=\"Iron Fleet\">Iron Fleet</a> and bring Dany to him, but Victarion means to take her to wife himself.\n</p><p>Victarion's shield hand was hurt fighting <a href=\"/index.php/Talbert_Serry\" title=\"Talbert Serry\">Talbert Serry</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Taking_of_the_Shields\" title=\"Taking of the Shields\">taking of the Shields</a>, and the wound has festered. Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Kerwin\" title=\"Kerwin\">Kerwin</a> has had little success treating the wound. Victarion learned that the strong <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantene</a> fleet is on their way to <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a> as well, while his own fleet was scattered on their way and only half have come back together.\n</p><p>The 54th ship to arrive, <i><a href=\"/index.php/Grief\" title=\"Grief\">Grief</a></i>, has happened upon <a href=\"/index.php/Moqorro\" title=\"Moqorro\">Moqorro</a>, who was swept overboard <i><a href=\"/index.php/Selaesori_Qhoran\" title=\"Selaesori Qhoran\">Selaesori Qhoran</a></i> when <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion</a> traveled her to Meereen. The <a href=\"/index.php/Red_priest\" title=\"Red priest\">red priest</a> claims to have seen in his flames that Victarion will die unless the priest helps him. Moqorro succeeds in healing him, and Victarion has the maester killed. Victarion makes for Meereen.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Characters_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Characters appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_56&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Characters appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Moribald_Chester\" title=\"Moribald Chester\">Moribald Chester</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tom_Codd\" title=\"Tom Codd\">Tom Codd</a> (Bloodless Tom)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dusky_woman\" title=\"Dusky woman\">dusky woman</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aeron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Aeron Greyjoy\">Aeron Greyjoy</a> (the Damphair)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Euron Greyjoy</a> (the Crow's Eye)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Burton_Humble\" title=\"Burton Humble\">Burton Humble</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kerwin\" title=\"Kerwin\">Kerwin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Moqorro\" title=\"Moqorro\">Moqorro</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Nute_the_Barber\" title=\"Nute the Barber\">Nute the Barber</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Longwater_Pyke\" title=\"Longwater Pyke\">Longwater Pyke</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ralf_the_Limper\" title=\"Ralf the Limper\">Ralf the Limper</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Talbert_Serry\" title=\"Talbert Serry\">Talbert Serry</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daegon_Shepherd\" title=\"Daegon Shepherd\">Daegon Shepherd</a> (the Black Shepherd)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Sparr\" title=\"Rodrik Sparr\">Rodrik Sparr</a> (the Vole)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ralf_Stonehouse\" title=\"Ralf Stonehouse\">Red Ralf Stonehouse</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wulfe_One-Ear\" title=\"Wulfe One-Ear\">Wulfe One-Ear</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_terms_mentioned\">Places and terms mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_56&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and terms mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Basilisk_Isles\" title=\"Basilisk Isles\">Basilisk Isles</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brindled_men\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brindled men\">brindled men</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Common_Tongue\" title=\"Common Tongue\">Common Tongue</a></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Dagon%27s_Feast\" title=\"Dagon&#39;s Feast\">Dagon's Feast</a></i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Disputed_Lands\" title=\"Disputed Lands\"